{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2435596, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 463982, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "3000/1500，难者不会，会者不难", "timestamp": 1630768919, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2435604, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 463982, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "1.新生一般是开学前两周（国庆前）完成体测，体育课的前两周课都是安排体测，体测结束后再分班上专项。\n2.每学年秋季学期体测一次，在秋季学期体育课总评里面占10分，只要体测总分及格就可以拿满10分，不及格的话按比例拿分。", "timestamp": 1630768966, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2435608, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 463982, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "1.一般第14周前后开始\n2.体质测试过60即可，过60即可拿到期末总评这一项的满分10分", "timestamp": 1630768983, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2435623, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 463982, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "啊我好像理解错题主说的1了，如果是体育课的身体素质项目（大一秋季是长跑、立定跳、跳绳）的话，那一般是期中之后考，第10周左右开始，15周之前考完。", "timestamp": 1630769053, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2435638, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 463982, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果你现在开始练长跑估计还有三个半月，足够提升很多。开学的那个一般来说只要你身高体重正常，不是所有体育项目都拉垮的一塌糊涂，肯定能过", "timestamp": 1630769144, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2435644, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 463982, "reply_to": 2435604, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 不及格按比例拿分，就是说最多不到6分？", "timestamp": 1630769218, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2435647, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 463982, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "体育课只要不翘课一般都不会挂", "timestamp": 1630769233, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2435657, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 463982, "reply_to": 2435623, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 就是说这三样可以练两个月多一点（9周），然后专项是到期末对么？", "timestamp": 1630769287, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2435669, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 463982, "reply_to": 2435638, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 正常是指。。能详细一点么，有点害怕", "timestamp": 1630769356, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2435670, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 463982, "reply_to": 2435644, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 是的。", "timestamp": 1630769357, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2435675, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 463982, "reply_to": 2435657, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 专项一般也不会到期末才考，一般12周左右开始考，会提供两三次考试机会，避免体育课因为恶劣天气取消以及同学身体不适等。", "timestamp": 1630769411, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2435680, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 463982, "reply_to": 2435669, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 可能是指BMI正常吗", "timestamp": 1630769440, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2435685, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 463982, "reply_to": 2435669, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 开学的体测就是高中那个体测模式啊，算加权分，高中能及格的话现在也一样能及格，难度很小。", "timestamp": 1630769496, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2435696, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 463982, "reply_to": 2435670, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 啊，那好奇怪，不会有人的分数在[6,10)之间了...", "timestamp": 1630769584, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2435707, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 463982, "reply_to": 2435696, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 这个项目就是这样的……只要合格就行。其实cz觉得没有变成二值赋分就不错了。", "timestamp": 1630769644, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2435737, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 463982, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "现在开始练可以有很大进步 cz大一上学期所有项目都是十八年来首次及格", "timestamp": 1630769850, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2436201, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 463982, "reply_to": 2435669, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 只要BMI正常这一项都是满分，可以有效平衡很多弱项了", "timestamp": 1630773976, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2441372, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 463982, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "谢谢各位", "timestamp": 1630848864, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 5, "pid": 463982, "reply": 18, "tag": null, "text": "本人今年（2021）大一新生，体育特别不好，想请教一下大家：\n1.学期体育测验是在什么时间，如果现在坚持练习的话能有几周练习时间？\n2.在第一，二周进行的那个测验会有多大影响？(因为这个明显来不及了）\n目标是希望能稳定地不挂体育\n非常感谢", "timestamp": 1630768827, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1630848865, "url": "", "vote": {}}}